name: Homemade Choco honeycrunch
description:
Gorgeously sweet, homemade Choco Honeycrunch is crunchy honeycomb covered in sumptuous milk chocolate.

Choco Honeycrunch is sold in 100g batches. 

Note: All confectionary is made as it is ordered, so it always arrives fresh. 
Full ingredients list is avaliable on request, list of ingredients are also sent with item.
Cannot garuntee products are nut free although produced in a nut-free environment.
All products are tax-free
